===Music video===
At the request of [[MTV]], the single was accompanied by a music video, directed by Arthur Pierson. The video took place in the garden of artist [[Howard Finster]], who would go on to paint the album cover for the band's second album, ''[[Reckoning (R.E.M. album)|Reckoning]]''.

